---
import { Button } from "@workspace/ui/components/button"
---

<section class="w-full bg-surface-container py-section-gap">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div class="relative aspect-square md:aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale" alt="A monochromatic art photograph of stacked textile samples in various shades of grey and black. The focus is macro, showing the intricate weave and superior quality of the fibers. The lighting is soft and diffused, creating a serene, gallery-like atmosphere that underscores the brand's commitment to material excellence." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCMQqllWbIHYs5OftTUi3jS3N4FtlPBIoJaZOZevXDSO11zOm72jsDV7z6VcJ9qQSetkUxhPdT-xDlrP8D-CH6HFsQSZX_AJ4OEXTu1QT5XinwsoA_AnTHDoj8P-kRgvpaLiUKsjwse_fEEj73V131JvswSvn0dBIesFD8LiqgzdpThcIylzOdphFJEg_dfqr9bMZr25p44y3h2ddSa2Zp4nQ3wKGPwFFkPxCdQ1_8ermvYvcH7yp8NOMWRGHO0qAb0STo90evCu-oo">
</div>
<div class="space-y-8">
<h3 class="font-display-xl text-headline-lg uppercase leading-tight">THE SILENT REVOLUTION OF FABRIC</h3>
<p class="font-body-lg text-black">
                        Our philosophy is built on the absence of noise. We remove the superfluous to reveal the essential character of every garment. Every stitch is a deliberate choice; every silhouette is an architectural statement.
                    </p>
<ul class="space-y-6">
<li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-black/10 pb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">verified</span>
<span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest uppercase">Ethically Sourced Raw Materials</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-black/10 pb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">architecture</span>
<span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest uppercase">Architectural Pattern Cutting</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-black/10 pb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl">history_edu</span>
<span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps tracking-widest uppercase">Timeless Design Longevity</span>
</li>
</ul>
<Button className="rounded-none h-auto px-12 py-6 bg-black !text-white font-label-caps text-label-caps hover:!bg-white hover:!text-black transition-colors border border-black">OUR MANIFESTO</Button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
